Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,抜け殻みたいな空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,如空壳一般的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,何を見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:14.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,目覚めた理由ですら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:14.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,就连醒来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,也都还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:22.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,信じることに酷く怯えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:22.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,畏惧着自己所相信之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,だって　全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,因为 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,捨てたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,都已经舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,こんな世界ならもう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:33.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,这种世界 干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:39.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,消えてしまえと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:39.50,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,消失不见就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:43.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,憎んでいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:43.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,憎恶着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,張り裂けそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,像是要裂开一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,信じでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,我相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:54.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　キミの声が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:54.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,你看 你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,僕を救うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:57.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:04.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,何度も呼び覚まずよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:04.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,不论多少次 都愿意把我唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:09.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,キミが教えてくれた想い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:09.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,你教给我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,そう何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,然后我也会 不论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,キミの名前を叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:18.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,都呼喊着你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:22.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,強くその手を握って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:22.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,用力握着你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もう離さない決して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,绝对不会再把手放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:28.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,どんな未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:28.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,不论什么样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:32.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,キミとなら逃げない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:32.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,与你一起的话都不会再逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.92,opjp,,0,0,0,,光見付けた 空白の時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.92,opcn,,0,0,0,,发现了光芒 空白的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.57,opjp,,0,0,0,,迷い込んだ 宙吊りの世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.57,opcn,,0,0,0,,误入了悬空的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:27.08,opjp,,0,0,0,,信じられる答え 探し求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:27.08,opcn,,0,0,0,,追寻着可以令人信服的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.08,opjp,,0,0,0,,ただ彷徨って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.08,opcn,,0,0,0,,只是彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.87,opjp,,0,0,0,,Yeah 夜の隙間　Make it a light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.87,opcn,,0,0,0,,Yeah 夜晚的间隙　Make it a light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.37,opjp,,0,0,0,,忙しいったら暇もない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.37,opcn,,0,0,0,,忙起来就没有空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:35.21,opjp,,0,0,0,,受けた傷跡さえ勝手にイメージ付きで冴えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:35.21,opcn,,0,0,0,,连受到的伤痕都随便地留着鲜明的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.67,opjp,,0,0,0,,誰も彼も DEAD OR ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.67,opcn,,0,0,0,,无论谁都是 DEAD OR ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.21,opjp,,0,0,0,,守るだけじゃ CAN'T SURVIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.21,opcn,,0,0,0,,只是守护的话 CAN'T SURVIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.01,opjp,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna lie to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:41.01,opcn,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna lie to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:42.67,opjp,,0,0,0,,Keep on the fight Get light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:42.67,opcn,,0,0,0,,Keep on the fight Get light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.22,opjp,,0,0,0,,I give a rousing cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.22,opcn,,0,0,0,,I give a rousing cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.59,opjp,,0,0,0,,Keep on the day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.59,opcn,,0,0,0,,Keep on the day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:46.55,opjp,,0,0,0,,Time to ride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:46.55,opcn,,0,0,0,,Time to ride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.51,opjp,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.51,opcn,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.22,opjp,,0,0,0,,I'll find my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.22,opcn,,0,0,0,,I'll find my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.85,opjp,,0,0,0,,Yeah,I'll never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.85,opcn,,0,0,0,,Yeah,I'll never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:53.81,opjp,,0,0,0,,Never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:53.81,opcn,,0,0,0,,Never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.52,opjp,,0,0,0,,Now nobody can stop me,no way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.52,opcn,,0,0,0,,Now nobody can stop me,no way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.48,opjp,,0,0,0,,忘れてしまうことのないように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.48,opcn,,0,0,0,,为了不忘记曾经的过往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.57,opjp,,0,0,0,,朽ちるもの全て　取り戻すため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.57,opcn,,0,0,0,,为了将腐朽的东西全部取回
